{
  "id": "adv_event_2310_01_01",
  "title": "最強コンビの\n最強ユニット",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん、大丈夫？　緊張してない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan‚ are you okay? Are you nervous?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.9788661957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.1921995481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "……な、なんともありませんわ\nいたって平常心ですから――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…N-no‚ I’m fine.\nI’m perfectly calm――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1921995481,
      "endTime": 9.860113461800001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.9467805386
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "こ～ちょこちょこちょこちょ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tickle‚ tickle‚ tickle‚ tickle~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9467805386,
      "endTime": 13.2488440037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.3155107022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "あははははは！？　ちょ、ちょっと、芽衣……！\n舞台袖で何を！　怒られますわよ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahahahaha!? H-hey‚ Mei…!\nWhat are you doing backstage?! We’ll get in trouble!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.3155107022,
      "endTime": 21.3603184224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.5336522263
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、ごめんごめん\nでも、力は抜けたんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ sorry‚ sorry!\nBut you feel more relaxed now‚ don’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5336522263,
      "endTime": 26.9767362755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.1834028086
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですわね\nまったく、いつも強引なんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re right.\nHonestly‚ you’re always so forceful!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.1834028086,
      "endTime": 33.5852847895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.7852847895
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、呼ばれたね。よーし！　行こっか、すずにゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ they’re calling us. Alright~! Let’s go‚ Suzu-nyan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7852847895,
      "endTime": 39.1551485857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.3618151189
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、かましてやりますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ let’s show them what we’ve got!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3618151189,
      "endTime": 42.361815166599996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――しばらく前のこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A while ago",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3684817952,
      "endTime": 44.5684817952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.5684817952
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "この辺りで休憩しよっか。よーし、ここでさっき買った\nドーナツとうじょ～！　はい、すずにゃんの分",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s take a break around here. Okay‚ time to bring out the\ndonuts we just bought~! Here’s yours‚ Suzu-nyan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5018161458,
      "endTime": 56.827734152699996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.4941628887
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.0210674288
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、芽衣",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks‚ Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.0210674288,
      "endTime": 58.594854331200004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.8081876597
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ……せーのっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay… Ready… set!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.8081876597,
      "endTime": 62.1481875739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.2748522442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いただきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s eat!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.2748522442,
      "endTime": 63.8299995821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.0166662296
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "あー……むっ\nんふー！　今日もドーナツは美味しいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aah… Munch\nMmm! Donuts are always so good!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.0166662296,
      "endTime": 73.8550792774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.0550792774
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "一仕事終えた体に染みますわね\nラジオのゲスト出演、うまくいって良かったですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s even more delicious after work.\nI’m glad the radio guest appearance went well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.0550792774,
      "endTime": 81.2316552242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.4183220626
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "双子みたいに息ぴったりだねって言われたねー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said we’re like twins‚ perfectly in sync~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4183220626,
      "endTime": 84.6119275333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.8052608094
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "双子は大げさな気がしますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Twins is a bit of an exaggeration…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8052608094,
      "endTime": 88.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.3021501465
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "えー？　芽衣は嬉しかったよ？\nすずにゃんは嬉しくなかった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~? I was happy!\nWeren’t you‚ Suzu-nyan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3021501465,
      "endTime": 93.5520140571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.7653473142
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "う……ま、まぁ、私達のトーク力を\n世に知らしめることが出来て良かったですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ I’m glad we were able to\nshow the world our talking skills.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.7653473142,
      "endTime": 101.2053505185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣との付き合いが一番濃密なのは私ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m the one who’s closest to Mei after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.3653510653,
      "endTime": 105.67764154310001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.8709748193
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "私と芽衣が話せばどう盛り上がるかなんて\n手に取るように分かりますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s obvious how exciting it would be\nif Mei and I talked together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8709748193,
      "endTime": 111.1402264519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.3535598997
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2310_01_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "おおっ！　頼もしい！　すずにゃんは芽衣博士ですな～\n芽衣達、最強コンビだね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh! That’s reassuring! Suzu-nyan is like expert of Mei~!\nWe’re the best duo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3535598997,
      "endTime": 120.4622442488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――That night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.4489065096,
      "endTime": 122.54890650959999,
